# Integration test: 08 — Pinned piece can still move along the pin line
# wR is pinned to wK by bR on rank 0, but sliding along that same rank
# (toward the attacker) keeps the king shielded, so it remains legal.
Board:
wK . . . wR . . bR
Commands:
click 0 4
click 0 5
print board
Expected:
wK . . . . wR . bR
